    "In the realm of algorithmic innovation, each AI generation both builds upon and necessitates new breakthroughs.",
    "LLMs mark a significant milestone in AI development, serving as a bridge between static generative models and dynamic, adaptive AI systems.",
    "By integrating multi-agent architectures, knowledge distillation, and self-optimization, LLMs move AI closer to autonomous, goaldirected intelligence, a defining characteristic of AI 4.0.",
    "However, as AI progresses toward greater autonomy, fundamental challenges remain.",
    "AI 4.0 would demand not only advanced RL and sophisticated planning but also frameworks for self-reflection, introspection, and emergent goal formulation."
